-- Chris Bosh to Join Dwayne Wade on NBA's Miami Heat
-- Erik Matuszewski
-- 2010-07-07T16:35:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/dwayne-wade-chris-bosh-announce-they-ll-play-for-miami-heat-next-season.html

          
          
             Dwyane Wade is staying with the Miami
Heat and Chris Bosh will join him.  
 Wade and Bosh were among the top free agents in the
National Basketball Association this offseason, along with
LeBron James. Wade has spent his entire seven-year career in
Miami, winning an NBA title in 2006, while Bosh played the past
seven seasons with the Toronto Raptors.  
 Wade and Bosh made the announcement on ESPN.  
          
          


  


        